title: Meet Google Home Max | Big help meets big sound
description:
Hear every note as the artist intended. Feel every beat with heart-pounding bass. Meet Google Home Max. It’s our ultimate speaker, made for your music. It's also our first speaker with Smart Sound, a new audio experience powered by Google’s AI.
